is not professional at all.

56
00:03:43,330 --> 00:03:44,330
No, I have to find them.

57
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:47,420
This is a huge deal, you know?

58
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:48,450
He can't be perfunctory.

59
00:03:48,540 --> 00:03:49,100
Don't do this.

60
00:03:49,111 --> 00:03:50,430
Don't cause other people trouble.

61
00:03:50,770 --> 00:03:51,100
Come.

62
00:03:52,170 --> 00:03:52,730
Let's go.

63
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:53,170
Let's go.

64
00:03:53,666 --> 00:03:54,320
That's the place.

65
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,090
The Western hall.

66
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:56,300
Tian, let's go.

67
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:57,420
Don't hold my hand.

68
00:03:57,610 --> 00:03:58,540
