73
00:04:09,650 --> 00:04:10,770
You're my girlfriend.

74
00:04:11,050 --> 00:04:12,920
You have to attend
different occasions with me.

75
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,090
What kind of occasion is this?

76
00:04:14,090 --> 00:04:16,300
Weddings and funerals
are all very important occasions.

77
00:04:16,330 --> 00:04:18,530
But I don't think
I'm dressed up for the occasion.

78
00:04:18,911 --> 00:04:20,090
You should've told me earlier.

79
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:21,770
I would've changed them.

80
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:24,060
There's no way
we can predict the future.

81
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:25,260
I think you look fine.

82
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:27,500
Let's go.

83
00:04:29,530 --> 00:04:31,500
They're so indecent.

84
00:04:32,577 --> 00:04:33,450
Just stay out of it.

85
00:04:33,688 --> 00:04:35,140
Do they even know where they are?

86
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:36,210
Yeah.

87
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:37,450
Dad.

88
00:04:37,970 --> 00:04:38,290
Dad.

89
00:04:38,533 --> 00:04:39,410
